author: The Current
description:
To celebrate The Current’s 20th Anniversary, The Current’s Live Sessions Vault unlocks never-before-seen live performance videos of bands and artists who have played in our iconic studio. 

Watch to see the full session of The Suburbs, featuring previously unreleased footage, from when they visited the The Current studio back in 2017.

Songs Performed 
00:00:00 Hey Muse
00:03:49 Lost You on the Dance Floor
00:07:44 When We Were Young

Musicians
Chan Poling – vocals, keyboard
Hugo Klaers – drums
Steve Price – bass
Janey Winterbauer – vocals
Steve Kung – trumpet
Max Ray – saxophone
Rochelle Becker — saxophone
Jeremy Ylvisaker – guitar
Steve Brantseg — guitar 

Credits
Engineer – Mike DeMark
Producer – Derrick Stevens
Visuals  – Nate Ryan
Digital Producer – Natalia Toledo
Graphics – Natalia Toledo

The Current’s Live Sessions Vault is supported by the Minnesota Orchestra, GS Motors, and Delta Dental of Minnesota Foundation.
